><p>therefore, i (candidate full), (PARTY NAME) candidate for president, pledge i shall not campaign or participate in any state which schedules a presidential election primary or caucus before feb. 5, 2008, except for the states of iowa, nevada, new hampshire and south carolina, as "campaigning" is defined by the rules and regulations of the dnc. it does not include activities specifically related to raising campaign resources such as fundraising events or the hiring of fundraising staff. </p></blockquote></span>



